name: #11 - Pandemonium
description:
(Unmute Sound for Optimal Experience)

Fragment 11 - Pandemonium
(From the BINARY EMOTIONS series)

"Embrace the pandemonium. Find happiness in the unique insanity of being here now. The mind is a blithering gush, a pandemonium of thoughts."

PANDEMONIUM: It's dedicated to not conquering content and to acting upon the idea of genes within those thoughts. Amidst the chaos are the ones that lead to unique discoveries as the consciousness dwells the wondrous, attaining the realm beyond the simple material.
--
"BINARY EMOTIONS" is a series based on 12 Single Edition Fragments in which the artist aims to translate his inner nuances within a specific moment into visuals that evoke certain emotions. An emotional journey digitized into a binary piece cataloged onto the blockchain.
